      "failure_message": "Requires panic as the primary signal (control-collapsing, high-arousal threat), grounded by high threat/arousal and low agency; explicitly excludes dissociation and numb shutdown and the freeze branch; fires only on a real panic onset (panic spike/crossing or a sharp drop in agency)."
